---

<section class="section">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="section-label">Why This Matters Now</div>
    <h2>The landscape is shifting fast.</h2>
    <div class="why-now-grid">
      <div class="fade-up">
        <p class="intro-text">In the last year:</p>
        <ul class="trend-list">
          <li>
            <div class="trend-arrow"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M7 14l5-5 5 5z"/></svg></div>
            Carrier requirements have tightened
          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="trend-arrow"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M7 14l5-5 5 5z"/></svg></div>
            Compliance conversations have increased
          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="trend-arrow"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M7 10l5 5 5-5z"/></svg></div>
            Ransomware recovery expectations have shortened
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="question-box fade-up">
        <h3>If you can't confidently answer:</h3>
        <ul class="question-list">
          <li>
            <span class="q-mark">?</span>
            "Could we recover quickly?"
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="q-mark">?</span>
            "Can we pass a carrier audit?"
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="q-mark">?</span>
            "When was our last documented review?"
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="clarity-line">This checklist will give you clarity.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .intro-text {
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--text-light);
  }

  .why-now-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 60px;
    margin-top: 48px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .trend-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .trend-list li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
    padding: 20px 24px;
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text);
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .trend-list li:hover {
    border-color: var(--orange);
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(244, 128, 33, 0.08);
  }

  .trend-arrow {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.08);
    border-radius: 8px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .trend-arrow svg {
    width: 18px;
    height: 18px;
    fill: #ef4444;
  }

  .question-box {
    background: var(--card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 40px;
    box-shadow: var(--card-shadow);
  }

  .question-box h3 {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  .question-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .question-list li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 14px;
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.5;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .question-list li .q-mark {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    background: rgba(244, 128, 33, 0.15);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--orange);
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .question-box .clarity-line {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--orange);
    padding-top: 24px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .why-now-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
    }
  }
</style>
